task.summary: Improved test so that it does not fail (if violations plugin is missing).
[FIXED JENKINS-21510] Use context path for ball images.
[FIXED JENKINS-21240] Improve regexp. Now missing class file warnings are also catched.
[ FIXED JENKINS-20070] Clear SAX system property afterwards.
[FIXED JENKINS-19689] Improved option resolve relative paths: Always concatenate workspace prefix and relative path suffix,
[FIXED JENKINS-21569] Expose current line in groovy. Added getCurrentLine() method for line based parsers.
[FIXED JENKINS-21569] Expose variable lineNumber in groovy.
